item.title: Family Fun Day on the Trail
item.description: Join your friends and neighbors on the South Tama Rec Trail for Family Fun Day on June 10, 2023! Our activities and schedule of events are subject to change. Check this page for updates as June 10, 2023 approaches. Directions and a list of scavenger hunt items is available to download using the "dinosaur" QR code in the poster, and paper copies will be available at the check-in station on June 10.

item.title: Steering Committee Meeting
item.description: The original committees from Tama and Toledo, and others who wish to join the effort, are invited to meet and discuss organization, priorities, and next steps. This meeting will be held in the Wieting Theatre Community Room. Agenda specifics: To be announced
